  The star wore a plunging black gown with a white, fanned out ruffle detail that furled around her hourglass figure. Priyanka stunned in the skintight ensemble, accessorising with an ornate, emerald necklace. She wore her hair in an elegant updo, allowing some strands to fall across her face. The actress, who welcomed a baby girl via surrogate with her husband Nick Jonas earlier this year, opted for a soft, smokey eye makeup look, and could be seen blowing kisses to the public as she made her way out to the car.   